== History == The B-nine are a cybernetic species created by [[A-six]]. They were emancipated by their creator on 16.11.55.343, allowing them to control their own reproduction.
The B-nine honor their biological creators and want to become like them.
== See Also == * [[A-six]] * [[Ancient Races]]
{{TEC}}

The Syrtis War was an interplanetary military conflict that began in the year 2230 with an attack on Earth colonies by the Syrtis sovereign on Mars. The war ended in 2251 after Commonwealth forces entered the Sol system and nuked Mars from orbit. It remains the bloodiest and most destructive conflict in human history, resulting in hundreds of millions of deaths, massive damage to all of Earth's major cities, and the destruction of the Syrtis civilization.

== Causes of the War ==
{Resentment over the gene crisis; rise of the Ares Sect; etc.}

